            <section class="case-block not-padded cds-narvik">
                <div class="inner-block half absolute-left vertical-center left-padded mobile-container"  data-sr>
                    <h2 class="case-block-text-heading short-length">We see branding with our eyes closed</h2>
                    <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">Our brand system passes an important test: it&rsquo;s simple enough to remember with your eyes closed. Leaving a strong impression often means being bold enough to keep it simple.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="inner-block half float-right full-height cds-red">
                    <img class="case-block-image" src="../images/cds/branding.svg">
                </div>
            </section>
            <!-- END case-block -->

            <section class="case-block extra-padded cds-dark-blue">
                <div class="container narrow">
                    <div class="inner-block one-third absolute-right vertical-center mobile-padded-above mobile-padded-below mobile-container-absolute"  data-sr>
                        <h2 class="case-block-text-heading short-length">A logo with deeper (and double) meaning</h2>
                        <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">Our tech audience may see their file URI (://) in our clever remix of the American flag.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="inner-block two-third float-left mobile-container-absolute relative">
                        <img class="case-block-image" src="../images/cds/logo.svg" data-sr="enter left, move 400px">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <!-- END case-block -->

            <section class="case-block-flex not-padded view-three-quarter">
                <div class="inner-block half float-left padded mobile-container-extra flex-center cds-blue">
                    <h2 class="case-block-text-blockquote medium-length">Brave UX feels like a true member of our team</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="inner-block half padded mobile-container cds-white flex-center">
                    <div class="container flex-col">
                        <img class="case-block-text-quote-icon align-left" src="../images/cds/quote.svg" data-sr="enter top, move 75px">
                        <p class="case-block-text-quote medium-length">The most important thing about Brave UX is partnership and empathy. Every other designer or design team I've worked with has felt like a business deal. Brave UX feels like a true member of our team, walking not just a mile in our shoes but a hundred in order to deliver the most spot-on us brand and designs I&rsquo;ve ever seen.  That is who they are and what they are all about, and what sets them leagues apart from the crowd.</p>
                        <p class="case-block-text-citation">Seamus Kraft, <em>Founder, Congressional Digital Service</em></p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </section>
